claim.claim-text:
The air conditioner according to any one of claims 1 to 11, further comprising:
a first earth line (5A) connected to the second filter unit (4, 4');
a first earth terminal (9A) connected to the first earth line (5A);
a second earth line (5B) connected to the ground; and
a second earth terminal (9B) connected to the second earth line (5B) and adapted to contact the first earth terminal (9A) and to be disconnected from the first earth terminal.
